{
  "texts": [
    "In the supervised training phase, label rebalancing is applied to adjust the loss regarding class infrequency.",
    "In the unsupervised phase, pseudo-labels are generated through pseudo-label calibration.",
    "The learning from unlabeled data is through the enforcement of consistency between the pseudo-labels and the predictions of instances augmented using SoftMix.",
    "where p is the pseudo-label generated for unlabeled input (see Equation (5)).",
    "ŷ is obtained by p yjΩ x u ð Þ À Á, where Ω x u ð Þ represents the prediction based on augmented variations of the question and the context (see section 3.4)."
  ]
}